#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/not.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.tensor.__not__"
msgstr "# triton.language.tensor.__not__"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/not.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/not.md:4
msgid "简介：对 tensor 做逐元素逻辑非（0 变 1，非零变 0）。对应 Python 的 `not` 关键字 —— Triton 通过 AST visitor 特殊处理，把 `not X` 重写为 `X.__not__()`。与按位取反 `~X`（见 [invert](./invert.md)）不同：前者是逻辑非，后者是按位翻转。"
msgstr "Introduction: Performs element-wise logical NOT on a tensor (0 becomes 1, non-zero becomes 0). Corresponds to Python's `not` keyword — Triton handles this specially via an AST visitor, rewriting `not X` as `X.__not__()`. This differs from bitwise inversion `~X` (see [invert](./invert.md)): the former is logical NOT, while the latter is bitwise flipping."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/not.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"# 通过 not 关键字（Triton AST 拦截处理）\n"
"not x\n"
"\n"
"# 或直接调用 dunder 方法\n"
"x.__not__()\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

